items.title: Scorching Indians land atop Power Rankings
items.summary: Now that we're in the midst of the real, true stretch run of the regular season, it's probably time to look at the weekly Power Rankings as the Postseason Power Rankings -- in other words, rank the teams by how likely it is they'll still be playing past Oct. 2, and how easy it will be for them to get there.

items.title: Position players pitching more than a fad
items.summary: By historical standards, the rate at which position players are handed the ball is beyond anything we've seen before in the big leagues. In 2017, position players have taken the mound 35 times.
